.TH "drm_crtc_vblank_waitqueue" 9 "drm_crtc_vblank_waitqueue" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
drm_crtc_vblank_waitqueue \- get vblank waitqueue for the CRTC
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "wait_queue_head_t *" drm_crtc_vblank_waitqueue
.BI "(struct drm_crtc *crtc "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "crtc" 12
which CRTC's vblank waitqueue to retrieve
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function returns a pointer to the vblank waitqueue for the CRTC.
Drivers can use this to implement vblank waits using \fBwait_event\fP and related
functions.
